        "content": "<p>Change the enriching category from <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathrm{Set}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Set</span></span></span></span></span> to something more amenable to temporal processes. </p>\n<p>Or take the notion or composition away from equality to an arrow of some kind.</p>",
